1. Express.js (Web framework for Node.js):
npm install express

2. Handlebars.js (Template engine):
npm install express-handlebars

3. MySQL (Database):
npm install mysql2

4. Sequelize (ORM for the database):
npm install sequelize

5. Express Session (User authentication):
npm install express-session

6. Connect-session-sequelize (Session store for Sequelize):
 npm install connect-session-sequelize
 
7. Passport (Authentication middleware):
npm install passport

8. Passport-local (Local authentication strategy):
npm install passport-local

9. Bcrypt (Password hashing):
npm install bcrypt

10. Dotenv (Manage environment variables):
npm install dotenv


